### Create reviews
# reviewer_id values assume user IDs were assigned in creation order above (1..4).
POST {{baseUrl}}/review/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mind-bending classic",
  "description": "Excellent pacing, visuals, and soundtrack.",
  "rating": 0.95,
  "media_id": 101,
  "reviewer_id": 1
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/review/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Still amazing",
  "description": "The action and ideas hold up very well.",
  "rating": 0.9,
  "media_id": 102,
  "reviewer_id": 2
}

### Optional sanity checks
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/get/1

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/review/get/101/1

